OL,3,CPeston: On welfare reform, Starmer and
OL,4,CReeves lose, whatever the outcome
OL,6,FSo given that on the current
OL,7,Ftrajectory, Starmer, Reeves and
OL,8,FKendall are heading for humiliating
OL,9,Fdefeat in just a few days, why not at
OL,10,Fthis late juncture just pull the
OL,11,Flegislation and roll its material
OL,12,Freforms into the autumn budget?
OL,14,FHere is the painful paradox. That
OL,15,Fstaged approach might well have been
OL,16,Fcredible in the spring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
