OL,3,CPeston: On welfare reform, Starmer and
OL,4,CReeves lose, whatever the outcome
OL,6,FNow such a delay might well say to the
OL,7,Fnation's creditors that Starmer,
OL,8,FReeves and co are weak and
OL,9,Fdirectionless - and that could lead to
OL,10,Fa painful rise in the interest rate
OL,11,Fpaid by the Treasury.
